snippet.title: Character Demo - "Chevreuse: Every Shot a Bullseye" | Genshin Impact
snippet.description:
Dealing with villains inevitably calls for some "special" approaches. Because of this, the Special Security and Surveillance Patrol is quite possibly the Palais Mermonia's least rule-abiding organization.
But fear not — Chevreuse only ever pulls the trigger when her own notion of "justice" is satisfied.
